Interface ElementInstance

All Known Implementing Classes:
BasicRandomizer, BlockRandomizer, ElementInstanceBase, ExperimentObjectInstance, FilterObjectInstance, Randomizer, TaskObjectInstance
public interface ElementInstance

    • nextTask

      Returns:
      A Future of the id of the next element
